          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Measurement of   the   photoneutron   cross   section",
                " 44Ca(g,sn) reaction (sn = n + np + 2n) has been made",
                " over the photon energy range 11 - 26 MeV. Comparison",
                " with 44Ca(g,p)  cross  section  shows  evidence  for",
                " isospin splitting  of  the  giant  dipole  resonance",
                " (GDR) in  agreement eith predictions.  some evidence",
                " has also been found for deformation splitting of the",
                " 44CA GDR."
              ]
            }
          ],
